Harry J. PearceAKA Harry Jonathan PearceBorn: 20-Aug-1942Birthplace: Bismarck, NDGender: MaleRace or Ethnicity: WhiteSexual orientation: StraightOccupation: BusinessNationality: United StatesExecutive summary: Vice Chairman of GM, 1996-2001Military service: USAF (Judge Advocate)Wife: (three children)    University: BS Engineering Sciences, US Air Force Academy (1964)    Law School: JD, Northwestern University School of Law (1967)    Administrator: Board of Visitors, US Air Force Academy    Administrator: Trustee, Howard University    Administrator: Trustee, Northwestern University    Bowman and Brooke Of Counsel
    General Motors Vice Chairman (1996-2001)
    General Motors EVP (1992-96)
    General Motors VP and General Counsel (1987-94)
    General Motors Associate General Counsel (1985-87)
    Pearce & Durick Partner
    North Dakota State Official Municipal Judge, Bismarck (1970-76)    Member of the Board of General Motors (1996-2001)
    Member of the Board of General Motors Acceptance Corporation 
    Member of the Board of Hughes Electronics (1992-2003, as Chairman, 2001-03)
    Member of the Board of Marriott (1995-)
    Member of the Board of MDU Resources (as Chairman)
    Member of the Board of Nortel (2005-, as Chairman, 2005-)
    Alliance of Automobile Manufacturers Board of Directors    American College of Trial Lawyers     Ashcroft 2000     Bush-Cheney '04     Economic Strategy Institute Board of Directors    George W. Bush for President     Gore 2000     Leukemia & Lymphoma Society Research Foundation President
    Mothers Against Drunk Driving Advisory Board    Marrow Foundation Board of Directors
    National Defense University Foundation Board of Directors
    US Council for International Business Trustee    World Business Council for Sustainable Development     Risk Factors: Leukemia





